author: @zaeeemyoi
text:
To Chaeyoung on the 3rd anniversary of your "Off My Face" cover:

Your voice in this song captured so much raw emotion and beauty. It felt intimate, like you were sharing a piece of yourself with the world. Three years later, it still moves us deeply, a reminder of your talent and the honesty you bring to every performance. Thank you for giving us a moment of vulnerability and art that continues to resonate. Here's to more music, more growth, and more heartfelt moments like this one. We’ll always cherish it. ❤

author: @llyza277
text:
just came across here again and feel like sharing my insights these past few months:

I'm genuinely happy for Chaeyoung. She has been recently getting the spotlight not just internationally but also within Korea. I noticed how she really shined starting from More and More (we could say it starts when they enter the US market). People start to recognize and give credit on her voice, on her english pronunciation, looks, and her overall skills. I started to notice that they're not only ONCEs but general kpop fans (mostly multi) and I couldn't be more happier that her being in a large group and constantly being overshadowed, she suprised many. 

I started to notice how her concept teasers are the most liked (if not, she's at least on the 2nd or 3rd most liked). Her photocards getting a lot of attention and considered as a hot pull for collectors. Knetz praising her for her shocking visuals as what they say (she's pretty everyone). Due to the shifting concept of TWICE, she's getting a lot of positive feedback for her vocals. 

I really hope all of these will continue and she'll have a strong fanbase of her own. A fanbase that can support her individual activity outside the group. And I also hope that this will be the start of her gaining back the lost confidence in their earlier years

author: @كيمهاينا
text:
العودة بكرا ونس فاكيد كلنا عارفين انو لازم نسوي س.ت.ر.ي.م بيوتيوب وسبوتيفاي ونسوي شازام ونصوت لتوايس بتطبيقات البرامج الموسيقية بس في كم شغلة اغلب الونس مايسسوها وحقولهم الحين
-اولا ال.س.ت.ر.ي.م مايقتصر عالامفي لا حتى الفانكامات كمان لانو البرامج الموسيقية ياخدو نسبة من م.ش.ا.ه.د.ا.ت الفانكامز وادائات الفنانين ببرامجهم
-برضو لازم ن.س.ت.ر.م بديزر وانغامي التطبيقين ثنينهم مهمين وماتقل اهميتهم عن سبوتيفاي خاصة ديزر سو لازم تحملوهم
-دعم كل المنشورات الي تتعلق بالعودة مهما كان الحساب الي ينزلها يعني لو صفحات الاخبار زي بوب بيز وحسابات الاخبار العربية نزلت عن العودة حندعم المنشورات كلها ونتفاعل فيها لو حسابات البيلبورد والامتيفي وغيرها من الحسابات الكبيرة نزلت عنهم برضو لازم نتفاعل فيها
-ضروري كمان نتفاعل بالهاشتاقات ونرفعها ونتفاعل بحساب توايس بتويتر فيسبوك انستغرام وتيكتوك هي كلها حترفع توايس بمخطط بيلبورد الاجتماعي

author: @tatilima6121
text:
If you are interested in playing this song in the guitar with Chae’s version you need to transpose the song from an E major to a G major (transpose 3)

So it will be like:
Capo 4th fret
Verse 1: D# G7 Cm A# (2x)

Chorus: D# G Cm A#
G# A# D# A#/D Cm A# (3x)
G# A#

Verse 2: D# G7 Cm A#

Chorus: D# G Cm A#
G# A# D# A#/D Cm A# (3x)
G# A#

Interlude: Cm Cm A#/D D# D#/G D# Cm A# (2x)

Chorus: G# A# D# A#/D Cm A# (3x) G# A#

Outro: G# A#

I hope this helps :)

author: @salmajuarez3769
text:
Me di la oportunidad de conocer a Twice gracias a Dahyun; pero Chaeyoung me robo el corazón y mirada cuando las vi a todas juntas, tiene una belleza muy única, y sus ojos se me hacen extremadamente hermosos. Lamentablemente con el tiempo me decidí por Jihyo y Mina como mis bias del grupo, y la dejé un poco de lado a ella, y me sentía mal por hacerlo:( fue algo que no pude evitar. Pero con este cover, me hizo sentir algo muy especial, que mi amor por ella que tenía al principio de todo esta regresando. 
Aunque no staneo a Twice, me gustan, las respeto y las admiro mucho. Este cover es demasiado hermoso como para no apreciarlo todos los días, tal como lo he estado haciendo desde que se lanzó de sorpresa ♡

If you're seeing this Chaeng, know that we, Onces, are really grateful to you for this wonderful ending gift for the anniversary week. author: @짱하준
text:
채영언니가 모두 좋은 하루 보내고 정리할 시간에 멜프가 나오니까 나오면 많이 들어달라고 해서
12시 딱 되자마자 올라온 채영언니 멜프를 보니까 다시금 느낀 게 채영언니는 도대체 못하는게 무엇인지 궁금해요..
전부터 열심히 준비한데다가 무리한 스케줄 사이에서도 멜프 준비해줘서 너무 고마워요
선곡 자체가 완전 채영언니스럽고 저음 노래에 이런 분위기가 너무 언니랑 잘 어울리는 것 같아요
요즘 너무 바쁠텐데도 버블도 자주 와주고, 오면 사진도 여러 장씩 올려주고, 인스타에도 사진 많이 올려주고, 브이도 해줘서 고마워요
앞으로 있을 7주년에는 6주년보다 더 행복하게 보내요!
언니 덕분에 입가에 미소가 떠나지 않고, 트와이스 덕분에 내 삶의 큰 위로를 받아요
채영언니가 이 댓글을 볼 지는 모르겠지만, 항상 건강하고 행복하고 이쁜 거 좋은 것만 보고 밥도 삼시세끼 꼭 잘 챙겨먹어요!
언니 멜프 너무 고마워요 찍느라 너무 고생 많았어요 너무 이뻐 ❤
청초여신 손채영!!✨

SON CHAEYOUNG HAS PROVEN SHE'S AN ACEE SINCE HER DEBUT. ARTISTIC, CHARISMATIC, AND EVERYTHING ELSE WAS TOTALLY PERFECT IN HER OWN MELODY PROJECT. THIS IS SON CHAEYOUNG WE KNOW FROM TWICE, SHE NEVER FAILED TO AMAZED US TO SHOW HER BIZARRE AND TALENTED SIDES.

WE ARE SO PROUD THAT OUR CHAEYOUNGIE IS NOW STEPPING OUT HER COMFORT ZONE AND SHOWING US HOW POWERFUL HER VOCALS CAN BE.

 ALL I CAN SAY IS "WOW" EVERY MINUTE AND SECONDS OF THIS MASTERPIECE. I WAS TOTALLY SPEECHLESS BECAUSE IT WAS SO BEAUTIFUL.

ARTIST CHAEYOUNG SUPREMACY! WE LOVE YOU OUR CHAEYOUNGIE! 🥺❤️

author: @justsomerandomperson1972
text: Chaeyoung is the most admirable person in TWICE to me personally. Besides her talents such as rapping, dancing to choreography and her angelic voice, her outside persona and character is what people mostly miss about her, yet it's the best thing about her. You can tell Chaeyoung's personality and character from her outside idol work, which is through her song writing, her fashion or even her little doodles that she often draws. She is never shy when it comes to expressing her thoughts, her intention, her liking which is not what we commonly see in your typical idols (not that there's anything wrong with idols that carry some certain images to appeal to the fans though).

Chaeyoung, I know my messages and comments will never reach you. But, I wanna express my feelings and thoughts about you before I go to sleep tonight.
